theorem positive_cone.one_pos (C : PositiveCone α) : C.pos 1 :=
  (C.pos_iff _).2 ⟨C.one_nonneg, fun h => one_ne_zero <| C.nonneg_antisymm C.one_nonneg h⟩
#align positive_cone.one_pos positive_cone.one_pos
